schema.description: A DoubleClick Search report. This object contains the report request, some report metadata such as currency code, and the generated report rows or report files.

files.description: Asynchronous report only. Contains a list of generated report files once the report has successfully completed.

byteCount.description: The size of this report file in bytes.

url.description: Use this url to download the report file.

id.description: Asynchronous report only. Id of the report.

isReportReady.description: Asynchronous report only. True if and only if the report has completed successfully and the report files are ready to be downloaded.

kind.description: Identifies this as a Report resource. Value: the fixed string `doubleclicksearch#report`.

rowCount.description: The number of report rows generated by the report, not including headers.

rows.description: Synchronous report only. Generated report rows.

statisticsCurrencyCode.description: The currency code of all monetary values produced in the report, including values that are set by users (e.g., keyword bid settings) and metrics (e.g., cost and revenue). The currency code of a report is determined by the `statisticsCurrency` field of the report request.

statisticsTimeZone.description: If all statistics of the report are sourced from the same time zone, this would be it. Otherwise the field is unset.

mappings.name: Generates and returns a report immediately.

rows.description: Synchronous report only. Generated report rows.

schema.description: A DoubleClick Search report. This object contains the report request, some report metadata such as currency code, and the generated report rows or report files.

files.description: Asynchronous report only. Contains a list of generated report files once the report has successfully completed.

byteCount.description: The size of this report file in bytes.

url.description: Use this url to download the report file.

id.description: Asynchronous report only. Id of the report.

isReportReady.description: Asynchronous report only. True if and only if the report has completed successfully and the report files are ready to be downloaded.

kind.description: Identifies this as a Report resource. Value: the fixed string `doubleclicksearch#report`.

rowCount.description: The number of report rows generated by the report, not including headers.

rows.description: Synchronous report only. Generated report rows.

statisticsCurrencyCode.description: The currency code of all monetary values produced in the report, including values that are set by users (e.g., keyword bid settings) and metrics (e.g., cost and revenue). The currency code of a report is determined by the `statisticsCurrency` field of the report request.

statisticsTimeZone.description: If all statistics of the report are sourced from the same time zone, this would be it. Otherwise the field is unset.

mappings.name: Retrieves a list of conversions from a DoubleClick Search engine account.

kind.description: Identifies this as a ConversionList resource. Value: the fixed string doubleclicksearch#conversionList.
